Author:  ANDERSEN
Vol / Page:  298
Edition:
Quote:  How, cowed and servile, gnawing hunger makes the soul-less frame to stagger, when at dim eventide the reeling form oft seeks to eat the refuse rori, cooked and left by Pare-korau!
